metadata.name: Sunflowers of Ukraine #1
metadata.description: Sunflowers of Ukraine is a symbolic collection of 10,000 unique digital collectibles in support of Ukrainian refugees, children, and victims of war. This collection reflects the values of peace, power, and prosperity for the Ukrainian people. Each sunflower collectible is an artistic representation of the beauty and cultural heritage of Ukraine. Proceeds will be donated to the Disasters Emergency Committee (DEC) Ukraine Humanitarian Appeal. Glory to Ukraine!ðŸŒ»
